    "For instance, for the edge primary_care_physicians_rate → life_expectancy, the simulated true causal graph will state: \"primary care physicians rate strongly affects life expectancy.",
    "\"Our objective here is not to construct the true causal graph, but to determine if when given quality data, RAG can be a useful option to reduce LLM hallucinations for auditing causal discovery.",
